room_title: Escape room "The Hollywood Mystery: A Room Noir" by Conundrum Escape Rooms in Denver
room_description:
The place is Hollywood. The year, 1948.

You are a private detective hired to protect the stars. One of your most famous clients has gone missing from her studio dressing room, leaving only scattered clues for the keen eye to find and piece together. It is up to you to find her kidnapper and save the damsel in distress, before it is too late!!
